	div(class='form-check')
		input(class='form-check-input' type='radio' id='radio2' name='answer' value='option2')
		label(class='form-check-label' for='radio2') Most of the time
	div(class='form-check')
		input(class='form-check-input' type='radio' id='radio3' name='answer' value='option3')
		label(class='form-check-label' for='radio3') Some of the time
	div(class='form-check')
		input(class='form-check-input' type='radio' id='radio4' name='answer' value='option4')
		label(class='form-check-label' for='radio4') A little of the time
	div(class='form-check')
		input(class='form-check-input' type='radio' id='radio4' name='answer' value='option4')
		label(class='form-check-label' for='radio4') Not at all